title: Adjust lottery and injection frequency
body:
We're proposing to adjust the current lottery and injection frequency.

Current frequency:
- 4x lotteries per day
- 1x 50,000 CAKE injection per day

Proposed new frequency:
- 2x lotteries per day
- 1x 100,000 CAKE injection every 2 days

We believe this will help to increase participation overall and increase the speed that it takes the pot to grow as a result.

The CAKE burn rate for both at no tickets bought is very similar, however, if the new frequency is able to generate higher participation then the amount of CAKE burned per day will increase significantly.
choices: 2x lotteries per day & 1x 100,000 CAKE injection every 2 days
